All For Latvia !
( Latvian : Visu Latvijai ! )
is a national conservative political party in Latvia .
All For Latvia !
started as a political youth organization in 2000 and became a political party in January 2006 , running in 2006 elections .
It won 1.48 % of vote and no seats in the parliament .
Its leaders are Raivis Dzintars and Imants ParƒÅdnieks .
All For Latvia !
supports making Latvian citizenship laws more restrictive for non-citizens .
The party is opposed to European federalism .
